# ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’» 2. Essence of Programming

Programming is the art of telling a computer **what to do** using logic and instructions.

### ğŸ§  Why Programming?

* Automate tasks
* Perform calculations
* Build systems
* Solve business problems

### ğŸ¯ Programming = Logic + Structure + Syntax

---

# ğŸ—‚ 3. Types of Programming Languages

| Category   | Examples          | What It Means              |
| ---------- | ----------------- | -------------------------- |
| Low-Level  | Machine, Assembly | Hardware-near instructions |
| High-Level | Java, Python      | Human-readable             |
| Procedural | C, Pascal         | Step-by-step flow          |
| OOP        | Java, C++         | Objects & classes          |
| Functional | Haskell, Scala    | Functions-first            |
| Scripting  | JS, Python        | Dynamic execution          |
| Hybrid     | Java              | Compiled + Interpreted     |

